{"title":"小弟弟　别生气","authors":["沈彭年"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小弟弟　别生气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（儿童小快板）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈彭年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小弟弟，别生气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥给你讲道理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈开的选举会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商量国家大事体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商量大事要仔细，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么能带我和你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要生气你快长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大以后进工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进工厂，开机器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选举大会你也去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要生气你快长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大以后到农场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农场去开拖拉机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选举大会你也去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要生气你快长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大以后保国防，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军，开飞机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选举大会你也去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小弟弟，别生气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥给你讲道理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道理讲得对不对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你也把意见提！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}